Order signed and filed.

THEREFORE, IT IS HEREBY ORDERED that Attorney Hagner's motion to withdraw as appointed counsel is held in abeyance pending the defendant's response as ordered;

IT IS FURTHER ORDERED that the defendant  shall respond within twenty (20) days of the date of this order by sending a letter to the court indicating how he will proceed, and if he chooses to proceed pro se, he shall address the four points in this order.
